<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/oct/06/">&#x27a0;</a> October 6, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="twitter-groovylinks" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://twitter.com/groovylinks">Twitter / groovylinks</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>I get annoyed with people who announce their every blog post in their Twitter feeds (if I&#8217;m interested, I&#8217;ll just subscribe to your blog). But curious to see if there&#8217;s a market for it, I&#8217;ve created a Twitter user which will announce new links on this site.  Follow &#8220;him&#8221; to get notified.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
