<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/sep/23/">&#x27a0;</a> September 23, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="twitter-tweettrak" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="https://twitter.com/TweetTrak">Twitter / TweetTrak</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Twitter&#8217;s &#8220;track&#8221; service (which texted you whenever a phrase was uttered) has been disabled for some time. Luckily, an enterprising soul has reimplemented it using Twitter&#8217;s search API, and it works a treat.  Follow @TweetTrak to get started.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
                    Filed under
                    
                        : <a rel="tag" class="tag" href="/tag/tweettrak/">tweettrak</a>
                    
