<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    <div class="flickrentry entry">
        <h4>Ahh good ol&#8217; Tricky Dick. #current</h4>

        <a href="http://flickr.com/photos/groovymother/2860320175/"><img class="flickrphoto" alt="Ahh good ol&#8217; Tricky Dick. #current" src="http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3217/2860320175_ceb65a6421_m.jpg" height="180" width="240" /></a>

        <p>
            <p>Screenshot from the Current TV <a href="http://current.com/debate">Hack the Debate</a> promo.  (Words put into my mouth by persons unknown).</p>

<p>Current will be screening the US presidential debates live on TV, with relevant tweets overlaid in real(-ish) time.  It promises to be a hell of an experiment (not least for our broadcast team!)  First debate: Friday September 26th.</p>
        </p>

